I admit I wasn't sure what to expect from this recipe but with all the good reviews I had to try it. We don't eat gluten anymore so I used gluten free penne. Also I don't eat beef so I used chicken-apple sausage (the kind like brats) instead. We have a bunch of homemade fermented sauerkraut so I drained it, but I didn't rinse. Funny thing is my husband doesn't usually like sauerkraut but he said the flavor wasn't strong enough to be noticeable. Success! We both like the recipe and we'll make it again.

