Rating: 3
Just want to comment on some of the other comments regarding pasta in this dish. My parents are originally Polish and my mom makes a version of this dish that has sauerkraut, pasta (wide noodles), and smoked ham/bacon in it. It's delicious. The combination may seem odd to some, but is in fact not so odd in other parts of the world. Enjoy.

